    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在第一周就筹集了 2 亿美元用于建立战争基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/harris-raises-200-million-in-first-week-to-build-up-war-chest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯作为 2024 年总统候选人的第一周就筹集了 2 亿美元，凸显了民主党对其新推定候选人的热情高涨，这也反映在民意调查中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/harris-raises-200-million-in-first-week-to-build-up-war-chest</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨未能推动德国经济起飞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/germany-economy-olaf-scholz-is-failing-to-engineer-a-liftoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国无法实现有意义的增长，给其经济的长期前景和总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导下的三个执政党的政治希望蒙上了一层阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/germany-economy-olaf-scholz-is-failing-to-engineer-a-liftoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉选举开始投票，可能引发重大转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拉加斯，委内瑞拉（美联社）——委内瑞拉周日将举行总统选举，其结果要么导致政局发生重大变化，要么使导致世界和平时期最严重经济崩溃的政策再延长六年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-28/venezuelan-election-could-lead-to-seismic-shift-in-politics-or-give-president-maduro-six-more-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 04:03:02 GMT</pubDate>
